attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a piece of rashult. He starts by screwing together the base frame, then the side legs, and then the top side legs. Next, he assembles the bottom grid tray by screwing it in. He does the same for the middle and top grid trays. Finally, he screws on the wheels and place the rashult on the floor.
